# SAP OData Configuration Examples

# Option 1: Specific Service URL (old format - still works)
# SAP_URL=https://your-server.com/sap/opu/odata/sap/API_BILLING_DOCUMENT_SRV

# Option 2: Base SAP System URL (new format - enables multi-service discovery)
SAP_URL=https://your-server.com/sap/opu/odata/sap
SAP_USERNAME=your_username
SAP_PASSWORD=your_password

# The system will automatically:
# 1. Extract base URL if you provide a specific service URL
# 2. Discover all available OData services
# 3. Allow intelligent switching between services

# Examples of discovered services:
# - API_CUSTOMER_SRV (Customer data)
# - API_BILLING_DOCUMENT_SRV (Billing documents)  
# - API_SALES_ORDER_SRV (Sales orders)
# - API_MATERIAL_SRV (Material master)
# - API_SUPPLIER_SRV (Supplier data)
# - And many more...
